HEADWORD: gruelling
<hw>gruelling</hw></mhw> <pos>adj.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>characterized by toilsome effort; requiring extreme
physical or mental effort; <as>as, a <ex>grueling</ex>
campaign</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> arduous, backbreaking, back-breaking, exhausting,
gruelling, hard, heavy, laborious, labourious, punishing, slavish,
strenuous, toilsome.</syn>⟦br⟧
